OL,3,CSocial media users 'complicit' in
OL,4,Criots that left 12 officers injured
OL,6,FSouth Yorkshire Police have confirmed
OL,7,Fthat 12 of their officers were injured
OL,8,Fafter rioters forced their way into a
OL,9,Fhotel housing asylum seekers.
OL,11,FAround 700 people were in attendance
OL,12,Fat the Holiday Inn Express in Wath-
OL,13,Fupon-Dearne, in Rotherham, when
OL,14,Fviolence broke out.
OL,16,FRioters smashed the windows of the
OL,17,Fhotel and attempted to set fire to the
OL,18,Fbuilding.
