OL,3,CSocial media users 'complicit' in
OL,4,Criots that left 12 officers injured
OL,6,FObjects including pieces of wood and
OL,7,Fchairs were thrown at police officers
OL,8,Flined up in front of the building,
OL,9,Fleaving one officer unconscious and
OL,10,Fothers with broken bones.
OL,12,FAssistant Chief Constable Lindsey
OL,13,FButterfield said that members of the
OL,14,Fcrowd who watched the violence were
OL,15,F"absolutely complicit" in it.
OL,17,FShe also said social media users who
OL,18,Fhad "spread misinformation and hate...
OL,19,Fneed to take responsibility for the
OL,20,Fscenes we saw".
