OL,4,Criots that left 12 officers injured
OL,6,FACC Butterfield continued: "This was
OL,7,Fnot a protest, just angry people,
OL,8,Freacting to a false narrative, shared
OL,9,Fby people who have their own
OL,10,Fmotivations for doing so."
OL,12,FSix person have been arrested, and the
OL,13,Fforce said officers would be reviewing
OL,14,Fimages and videos shared online to
OL,15,Ftrack down more offenders.
OL,17,FThey also said a heavy police presence
OL,18,Fwould remain outside the hotel and in
OL,19,Fthe surrounding area.
