OL,6,FSouth Yorkshire mayor Oliver Coppard
OL,7,Fsaid: "The police officers on the line
OL,8,Fhere were the bravest of the brave.
OL,10,F"There were 10 police officers
OL,11,Finjured, a police horse was injured,
OL,12,Fthose people were facing bricks and
OL,13,Fmortar being thrown at them by people
OL,14,Fintent on violence."
OL,16,FMr Coppard, who is also the police and
OL,17,Fcrime commissioner, said the offices
OL,18,Fwho were hurt suffered "significant
OL,19,Finjuries" including fractures.
